      "abstract": "Inject 3: containment, investigation and wider exposure assessment",
      "content": "Initial review indicates the email originated from a spoofed or deceptive source rather than the CFO's legitimate mailbox, but investigators cannot yet rule out mailbox compromise elsewhere in the executive support chain. The bank must determine whether this was a standalone social engineering attempt or part of a broader campaign targeting finance personnel and approval workflows.",
