      "abstract": "Inject 4: outcome, recovery and reporting",
      "content": "The bank receives partial feedback from external institutions: the transfer may be frozen in time, partially recovered, or moved onward before a full hold was placed. Leadership requests a decision on communications, regulatory notification, customer impact assessment, and post-incident remediation.",
